title: Paris parties all night with silent disco, art shows
text:
> Entertainment Paris parties all night with silent disco, art shows Participants wear headsets during a silent disco at the railway station Gare du Nord, turned into a giant nightclub, at the 14th edition of the Paris cultural event "Nuit Blanche," or "Sleepless Night," in Paris early Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015. (AP Photo/Kamil Zihnioglu)
